Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:05.88,Housei,,0,0,0,,I want to summon up all of my 46 years of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:13.49,Title White R,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1355,218)}Narrator:\NYamada\NShinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:15.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}For Housei's 46 birthday he's doing a 24 hour long interview!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Speaking about his whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:22.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he will talk for 24 hours straight, this is a new challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:27.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Loads of unknown stuff from his past!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:31.41,Housei,,0,0,0,,When I was in middle school, I bought like 'eccentric clothing for delinquients'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:35.08,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Are you mucking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:37.42,Housei,,0,0,0,,I formed the band in 1st year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:37.42,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\pos(713,827.333)\fad(200,0)}7 HOURS SINCE THE START
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:39.82,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,1072.667)}What kind of activities did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:43.46,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1056.667)}We performed in a studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:47.79,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1214,810)}In front of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.79,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,Well, we didn't perform in front of people but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:56.77,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(714,912.667)}The interview continues without rest for 15 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time seems to stop for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:13.02,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,898)}An emotional episode about Tsukitei Happo\Ngetting him into the Kyoto Rakugo Association
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:59.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As he starts to reach his limit, he continues to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then in the middle of his massage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:05.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he talks about how Tsukitei Happo defended him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,whilst the other rakugoka's were against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:12.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He tells us a touching story of how he got to be a rakugoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:16.76,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,1056.667)}"If Housei does something wrong, I'll quit"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:21.06,Housei,,0,0,0,,For him to do that much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:23.13,Housei,,0,0,0,,I've never thought it was possible for someone to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:26.03,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Those are some disgusting tears, eh!?
