Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.11,Housei,,0,0,0,,She's just so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.12,Housei,,0,0,0,,Her kindness is just{\alphaFF} so deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.75,Housei,,0,0,0,,Her kindness is just so deep.
