Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.91,Housei,,0,0,0,,I think if I did it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:53.18,Housei,,0,0,0,,「ＨＯＵＳＥ{\alphaFF} - i 」。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.72,Housei,,0,0,0,,「ＨＯＵＳＥ - i 」。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.56,HamadaC,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,278)}Oh I don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.96,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1047,499.333)}What about the image of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:10.37,Housei,,0,0,0,,Coco Chanel herself said what the best colour was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.97,Housei,,0,0,0,,Black,{\alphaFF} this is the best colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.84,Housei,,0,0,0,,Black, this is the best colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.57,Housei,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:22.95,Housei,,0,0,0,,HOUSE-i would have to have the 'best colour.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.82,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,So what colour would that be for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.85,Housei,,0,0,0,,I think it's got to be black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.72,MatsuC,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,278)}The same!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.19,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,So it would look a lot like Chanel clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.16,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah but there is no other colour...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.79,Housei,,0,0,0,,Well HOUSE-i is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:39.60,Housei,,0,0,0,,not Coco Chanel's rebirth or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.93,Housei,,0,0,0,,but I would want to go with black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.34,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,Since we are now talking about fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.44,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,when you look back on your life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:52.14,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,there were a few stories about your fashion\Nchoice so I just want to touch on that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.88,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(706,926)}So in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.88,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,you were wearing 'eccentric clothing for delinquents'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.45,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,After that,{\alphaFF} you were a surfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.32,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,After that, you were a surfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.32,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,936.667)}Yea, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:04.02,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,1067.333)}A complete surfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.43,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1257,1056.667)}What was\Nthe fashion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.43,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,Trainers of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:11.20,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,Weren't you too hot wearing trainers on a beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.77,EndoC,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,278)}What the hell...\NA surfer wearing\N trainers....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.64,HamadaC,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,278)}What the\Nhell is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.64,EndoC,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,390)}Whenever it gets\Nbad he goes to \Ndrink something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.14,TanakaC,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,278)}Since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It looks like when things are\Ngetting bad you go for a drink huh~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:32.48,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(704,846)}When this interview is over why don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:32.48,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}phone your wife and tell her how happy you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:36.25,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,Yea, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.52,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}What do you think your wife is going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.59,Housei,,0,0,0,,She'll be like "Oh my god, great work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.83,Housei,,0,0,0,,that must have been so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.67,Housei,,0,0,0,,But seriously, great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:51.07,Housei,,0,0,0,,What time are you coming home today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.04,Housei,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:56.87,Housei,,0,0,0,,Tonight I have my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.21,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,Were you the type of person to always accomplish his goals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:02.38,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,Like 'Once you start, you always accomplish it'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:06.05,Housei,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:10.66,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,926)}And that's why for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:10.66,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,I've never finished a jigsaw puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:17.43,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,99.333)}Fukuwarai - 'Lucky Laugh' a game\Nsimilar to Pin The Tail On The Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.93,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,So the Fukuwarai you're doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.93,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,928.667)}Fukuwarai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.43,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,Were you not playing Fukuwarai with your daughters...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.20,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,Wait I'm wrong... What was that jigsaw puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.24,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.57,Housei,,0,0,0,,'The Seven Deities of Good Luck.'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.57,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,923.333)}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.74,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,Sorry, when we carried on speaking after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:35.71,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,I just got really sleepy there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:42.42,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean I'm not really surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:50.86,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(724,712.667)}23 hours and 46 minutes since the start
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:51.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally we visit the moment of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:56.17,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,And now, finally we have nearly finished the 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.17,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,832.667)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:11:01.01,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,This really is the last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718,923.333)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:07.71,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}What do you feel looking back on this whole experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:10.08,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,Looking back on it I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:13.82,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd talk about my wife so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.69,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}I think, I was saved{\alphaFF} by my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.26,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,I think, I was saved by my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.29,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}My wife and I {\alphaFF}are the protagonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.90,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,My wife and I are the protagonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:32.27,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,My fate is my wife's fate and my wife's fate is my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:36.11,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,942)}If my wife is working hard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.11,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'll work just as hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.41,Housei,,0,0,0,,The philosophy I just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.84,Interview Question,,0,0,0,,my wife shares the same view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.31,Housei,,0,0,0,,I consult first with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.95,Housei,,0,0,0,,Everything is my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.79,Interviewer2,,0,0,0,,There's a saying 'If you're going to die, die on stage'...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:53.26,Housei,,0,0,0,,Well I've never thought I would die on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:58.13,Housei,,0,0,0,,When that happens, I want my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:01.50,Housei,,0,0,0,,at least my wife, by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:05.24,Housei,,0,0,0,,I guess the stage is fine, as long as she is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thing he learned from this challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is his deep love for his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.65,Black,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.16,Black,,0,0,0,,24 hours is up,{\alphaFF} congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:29.56,Black,,0,0,0,,24 hours is up, congratulations!
