Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1059,1040.667)}Uwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.56,Housei,,0,0,0,,There is a character count of{\alphaFF} 225,037 characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:13.06,Housei,,0,0,0,,There is a character count of 225,037 characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.57,Housei,,0,0,0,,Because a normal novel contains 70,000 characters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.90,Housei,,0,0,0,,this is 4...{\alphaFF} No 3 times more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.80,Housei,,0,0,0,,this is 4... No 3 times more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.94,Housei,,0,0,0,,Wait a second Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.94,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.34,Housei,,0,0,0,,Please try reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:27.18,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs(60)}Because of the Baby Boom Age, there were too many for one class~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:27.98,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,In 1st year was there 8 classes... {\alphaFF}Or 9 classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.25,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,In 1st year was there 8 classes... Or 9 classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:33.58,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was 10 classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,899.333)}How many were there then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.95,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Well, this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.09,Housei,,0,0,0,,No, no, please read more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.09,Matsu,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.06,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I've already watched enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.23,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's all actually been written here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.76,Housei,,0,0,0,,Well then, with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.70,Housei,,0,0,0,,I'm publishing a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.57,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(571,884.667)}Of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.57,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(910,875.333)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:56.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So you are asking if someone wants to publish that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.14,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,782)}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So you're going to ask them to contact you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.98,Matsu,,0,0,0,,That's completely different to what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.78,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It's totally different...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.95,Matsu,,0,0,0,,So get this published, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.88,Matsu,,0,0,0,,But what are you going to do with this, if no one wants to publish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.92,Housei,,0,0,0,,But this, I somehow want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:15.33,Matsu,,0,0,0,,As it is now, why don't you stick it in the\Ndrawer beside the bed in hotel rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.03,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Instead of the bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.70,Housei,,0,0,0,,Instead of the bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.06,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It'll be a hotel guideline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.57,Housei,,0,0,0,,They'd be surprised huh? Thinking "What is this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.97,Housei,,0,0,0,,To all the publishers who may want to publish this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.24,Housei,,0,0,0,,I will be waiting to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:34.68,Housei,,0,0,0,,Everyone here will do their best promoting the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.68,Housei,,0,0,0,,So please, I am counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.69,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(702,739.333)}5 Minute Free Talk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.69,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When did you cry recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,We've got a postcard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:52.03,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs59\pos(712,843.333)}Hello everyone, when I was watching the Olympics,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:52.03,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs59}I saw the various skills and abilities of people like Mao Asada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:56.40,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs59}It gave me a rush of emotions and I cried a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:16:05.81,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs59\pos(720,840.667)}Lately, I've had the feeling you guys cry at more things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:16:05.81,Thin Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs59\}have you cried at the Olympics or at anything in your daily lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.81,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is like serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.78,Endo,,0,0,0,,Not like the person who wrote this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Like properly crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,I was watching unedited footage of the opening ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.69,Endo,,0,0,0,,on the television in real time of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:16.32,Matsu,,0,0,0,,The Olympics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes, the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,They lit the Olympic torch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.29,Endo,,0,0,0,,and you know they do that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.13,Endo,,0,0,0,,Then finally it was lit but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.13,Endo,,0,0,0,,at that time I sort of leaned forward out of my kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.77,Endo,,0,0,0,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:33.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Because of all the tension at that time,\NI don't know if I'd call myself easily brought to tears but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.74,Endo,,0,0,0,,I cried!
