Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.78,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was with Hamada for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:50.05,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Actually I want to talk about something a bit different...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.82,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I remembered this recently, and during middle school…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.73,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was with Hamada for ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.66,Matsu,,0,0,0,,and we were at someone's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:01.47,Matsu,,0,0,0,,{\pos(742,910)}We were watching the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:01.47,Matsu,,0,0,0,,closing ceremony of high school baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.24,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Closing ceremony, that's what it's called, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:10.14,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Hamada was like "I want to watch the closing ceremony."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734,899.333)}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.21,Matsu,,0,0,0,,And I{\alphaFF} had no idea at all why he wanted to watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:14.15,Matsu,,0,0,0,,And I had no idea at all why he wanted to watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.81,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Like why the hell do you want to watch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:20.79,Matsu,,0,0,0,,And this program called 'Our Journey' was on at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.89,Matsu,,0,0,0,,something like that anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Like a drama series...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.66,Matsu,,0,0,0,,And I really wanted to watch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.59,Matsu,,0,0,0,,He was like "No no, Mattsun, just no."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.33,Matsu,,0,0,0,,We're obviously going to watch the\Nclosing ceremony of the high school baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.33,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was like what the fuck!?\NI thought he was kidding at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.60,Matsu,,0,0,0,,There's no way someone would\Nwant to watch a high schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.81,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Like literally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.87,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was thinking "How could you want to watch that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:47.45,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It was like the first time ever we nearly got in a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.01,Matsu,,0,0,0,,When I think about it now, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:53.25,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Like why the hell did you want to watch that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.62,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Obviously, we should've watched 'Our Journey'...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get you... When I think about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.83,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you want to watch it then!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I wonder what made me want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.59,Housei,,0,0,0,,And it was the closing ceremony as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.03,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It was, yeah... And then
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.93,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was like, "Wait, are you serious?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.53,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Like, "What is fun about that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.07,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But before it, isn't there the actual final?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.94,Black,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.94,Matsu,,0,0,0,,No, the final had already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.27,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.27,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, so..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:17.17,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So the winners and losers came together and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:17.17,Matsu,,0,0,0,,No, that finished as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.64,Matsu,,0,0,0,,The final finished and it was like "Okay, it's finished"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.01,Matsu,,0,0,0,,And to be honest, I don't really care too much\Nfor high school baseball anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.28,Matsu,,0,0,0,,And I was like "Okay, great, 'Our Journey'\Nis about to start on TV so let's switch the channel"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.52,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You were like "Just no... Let's watch the closing ceremony"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.19,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You were like "Just no... Let's watch the closing ceremony"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.99,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was like, no, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.26,Matsu,,0,0,0,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.23,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You were like, "No, just no... Seriously, just no..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.26,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I'm serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:42.43,Endo,,0,0,0,,Obviously there was a reason he wanted to watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:42.43,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was like, "What the hell!! He's messing with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.77,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.40,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You were like, "Obviously I want to watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.04,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Everyone was trying so hard..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.47,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.51,Matsu,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,790)}"Everyone was trying so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.51,Matsu,,0,0,0,,and the winner has been decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:55.41,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Obviously I want to watch the closing ceremony..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.18,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.75,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I was like "WHAT...!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Maybe I wanted to see the reaction and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.79,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(224,1063.333)}Maybe that was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.79,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1048,1056.667)}Yeah and he wanted to watch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.79,Matsu,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,978)}No way would you want to watch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.12,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Who gives a shit about the aftermath...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.56,Matsu,,0,0,0,,To this day, I do not understand the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:14.17,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember what actually happened that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.27,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I just can't shake it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,You were about to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:20.60,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.07,Matsu,,0,0,0,,We were literally so close to a full on fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.38,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I asked so many times, "But why, just why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.31,Matsu,,0,0,0,,He would just answer, "'Cause everyone tried so hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:32.72,Title White L,,0,0,0,,{\pos(817,856.667)}Tanaka's scary first meeting with Hamada!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:30.11,Endo,,0,0,0,,"They tried so hard"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh just cut it out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.09,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:37.09,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,talked to us about when
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.99,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:45.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Does everyone here like remember how they felt when meeting each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.73,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So for example, when Housei-san met Downtown...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.67,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Like your first impressions of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.67,Housei,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,What was it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.47,Housei,,0,0,0,,The second chome theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:56.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:56.51,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,899.333)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,You were on that program 'It's 4pm apparently'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:20:01.65,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,132.666)}* Broadcast from April 6, 1987\Nto September 29, 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,896.667)}That far back huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,The time of that program?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.71,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, "It's 4pm apparently" was starting to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:07.55,Matsu,,0,0,0,,So we were like 23, 24 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:07.55,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.05,Housei,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:14.09,Housei,,0,0,0,,you met me next to the corridor next to the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.66,Housei,,0,0,0,,And I said "Good morning", you were like "Oh, morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:20.03,Housei,,0,0,0,,You were a bit scary but you said "Oh, morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.07,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Oh, he didn't run and try and hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell, why would I hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.67,Housei,,0,0,0,,He was just like "Oh, good morning"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.67,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How about Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:30.27,Housei,,0,0,0,,He was in his dressing room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,and was reading a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:35.08,Housei,,0,0,0,,And when I said, "Good morning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,He was like, "Yeahhh"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Damn... You wouldn't even look him in the eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.55,Endo,,0,0,0,,Damn that's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.59,Endo,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't even look you in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:48.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,When I first said my greetings to Hamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.93,Endo,,0,0,0,,We were filming for Gaki at Sanseido...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.40,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,And we finished the opening and we went to say hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,I mean my part didn't get into the final edit that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:03.11,Endo,,0,0,0,,So we were at the car park, waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,And Hamada-san walked in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,We were like, "Good morning"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:10.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,He didn't even look at our face and just said "Yeah"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.38,Matsu,,0,0,0,,He does that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,899.333)}Like I remember it so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:16.39,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You should definitely look them\Nin the eyes and say hello at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:17.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That goes for you too then!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.06,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You'd think that's common sense, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:24.53,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was told that I was going to be on Gaki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.93,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,and they told me, "From next week."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:31.57,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(736,904.667)}And the week before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:31.57,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I went to introduce myself to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:33.67,Matsu,,0,0,0,,But I had already met you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.21,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, Matsumoto-san, you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.21,Matsu,,0,0,0,,At Tokyo station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.21,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:41.58,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,for the first time, I went to introduce myself to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,894)}Oh, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.65,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I said "My name is Cocorico and I will\Nbe working with you from next week."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:48.19,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"My name is Tanaka..." That is what I was going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:52.59,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And as I said "Oh, I am Cocorico's Tanaka...\NI will be working with you from next week..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.66,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,You had already walked off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:58.33,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Just as a human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:58.33,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Don't take the piss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:02.47,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was literally just like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:02.47,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I hate people like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.30,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I really hate people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.20,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It makes me want to quit Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:09.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Surely you don't feel that strongly about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:12.01,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It's important though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:13.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I was probably in a rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.48,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah probably, I was stuttering a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:17.41,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,In my first and second year...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.32,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Along with 'All Hanshin Kyojin'
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:21.75,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,when I was meant to introduce myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:24.02,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was just so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:25.96,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Before I introduced myself to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.39,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was thinking in my head,\N"You're introducing yourself to All Hanshin Kyojin"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.26,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So I knocked and said "Excuse me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:35.43,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I said "Nice to meet you, I am All Hanshin Kyojin"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:36.93,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I just freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:39.44,Matsu,,0,0,0,,That's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:40.74,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I really freaked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:40.74,Housei,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:44.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,If they had taken that the wrong way they could've\Nbeen like "Who does this punk think he is...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:45.34,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,They hadn't heard what I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:47.78,Endo,,0,0,0,,No no no, that wasn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:47.78,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:48.95,Endo,,0,0,0,,They reacted to what you said in your favour...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:48.98,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:52.02,Endo,,0,0,0,,They said "That's US!" to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:54.42,Housei,,0,0,0,,That was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:55.25,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,992.667)}No, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:58.26,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Forget that, your impersonation of him was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:00.46,Housei,,0,0,0,,What is with that high quality??
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:01.26,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,910)}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:04.13,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Surely you didn't need to make that impersonation that good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:05.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,Was it really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:05.70,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.53,Endo,,0,0,0,,He said "That's US" whilst laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:09.93,Matsu,,0,0,0,,No, the one before was better!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:11.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:12.97,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he said that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.97,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Was it? I was just so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:19.38,Matsu,,0,0,0,,So he must have thought,\N"Oh, this poor kid must be so nervous"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.08,Matsu,,0,0,0,,and reacted to make you less nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.31,Endo,,0,0,0,,That was probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:23.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:25.35,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they could probably\Ntell you were just nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:26.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And Hamada-san as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:30.25,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I had just watched you always on TV and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:32.99,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was to introduce myself to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.06,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was like in the same state...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was like so nervous and seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.93,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was so close to saying,\N"Nice to meet you, I'm Hamada."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.93,0:23:43.97,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I just held back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.97,0:23:46.07,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,and panicked at the time...
